vote.title: Authorize a twenty-year license agreement with one five-year renewal option, subject to Park and Recreation Board approval, with Lessee Main Street Investors Joint Venture and/or its successors and assigns of approximately 1,818 square feet of parkland located at 1516-1518 Main Street to be used for the operation and maintenance of an existing second and third floor balcony, an existing ground level patio area, and additional park enhancements - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
